including integration of Automated Test and Re-Test (ATRT), Model-Based Systems Engineering, Customer
Resource Management, Cybersecurity, Force-Level Integration and assessment, Collaboration boards, Agile/
Sprint tools, Software CM tools, and other virtual- and cloud-based tools to lower the barrier of entry for new
small businesses and startups. Digital environment will directly map to the Innovation Operations pipeline and
support the transition and development of new technology solutions.
