D. Acquisition Strategy
Explosive Saftey and Weapons Assessment is assigned as a non-ACAT program and therefore does not have program milestones like the ACAT I to IV programs. IMAD
develops and evaluates IM technologies for use in Navy weapon systems and is not part of a particular weapon acquisition program.




