Description: Enable innovation in our supply chain processes in the areas of data sciences, logistics IT
application development, and quality engineering through incorporation of Science, Technology, Engineering,
and Math (STEM) projects performed by interns and academia.

Perform market research on emerging supply chain technologies and methods that could be adopted to support
