and system development, manufacture, testing and field on submarine host platforms. Engagement with industry will support development of systems for enhanced
submarine capability via competitively awarded contracts (e.g., Family of Systems UUV Indefinite Delivery Indefinite Quantity (IDIQ) Contract. These vehicles will
facilitate requirements development, system development, and payload production to allow rapid integration into existing ship baselines.

(U) Bootstraps loosely follows the Middle Tier Rapid Fielding pathway leveraging existing contracts with performers.




